abstracts.cdata!:
The Vocational Training Project Loan for
            Dominican Republic was approved by the Board in May 1985.
            The loan was terminated by the Bank in November 1986, after
            failure to obtain congressional approval of the project, a
            national requirement for all externally-assisted projects
            before a loan can become effective.
